 "remarks": "2 bed, 1.5 bath end-unit townhome nestled in a well-maintained and quiet West Norwalk association. Enter into a living room with recessed lighting and crown molding. The eat-in kitchen opens up to a deck perfect for sunbathing, dining al fresco, or enjoying your morning coffee. A powder room completes the first floor. Upstairs is the primary bedroom with pull-down stairs to additional storage in the attic. A comfortably-sized second bedroom and full bath complete the second floor. The lower level features the laundry area, private garage, and a spacious storage room. Well run, self managed condo association with low HOA and pool! Conveniently located near Oak Hills Park, featuring a public 18-hole golf course, walking trails, and tennis courts. Screen door to be replaced by HOA",
